dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents roads for Iowa County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Iowa_Roads_2015.gdb'. [This data set consists of the road network for Iowa County, Wisconsin.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for students, faculty, and staff of the University of Wisconsin System for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data was produced to be suitable for use with Bullberry Systems, Inc. R³GIS Dispatch and Administrator 911 routing software, and other routing software based on an ESRI platform with Network Analyst extension.]
